Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After realizing the purity of his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hearing about his fight \Nagainst the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock finally came to trust Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Saving Ace! The Next Stop: \Nthe Great Prison!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really gonna give me a ride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I wouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! It doesn't have to be \Na great boat as long as it sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Departure will be tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuja Pirates will give you a \Nride to the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! By our pirate ship?\N--Sorry to be a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest well tonight to prepare for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to get off this island tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna see everybody soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. What a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonia! Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invite Luffy to tonight's banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A man to our banquet?!\N--Big Sis, that's too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Didn't you understand what I said?\N--Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a banquet to celebrate the Kuja \NPirates' safe return with a big haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got any food at this banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to one in \Na while! Yes!! A banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. You'll give me a ride and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hardly believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he mean he can hardly believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banquet! Banquet! Banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that Snake Princess \Nwould trust him this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dinner time!! A banquet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of good food! \NAren't you gonna eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll eat yours, \Nalright? Oh, you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he'll leave tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men's bodies are strange as the rumors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it at the arena. They can \Nstretch their legs really long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get my hands on Luffy-sama \Nto see how much he can stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"Luffy-sama"?\N--That's his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unthinkable to address \Na man in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the rule of Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why is Luffy-sama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a man who once got the \Ndeath sentence here, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of all places, our celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Snake \NPrincess has forgiven him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a trap laid by Snake Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He surprised them at the arena by putting \Nup a fight so she wants him to eat a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and catch him off guard and give him hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's our role to give him hell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take care of the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's starting to act strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Did he notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Screw you people!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sensed the trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he wants to fight us \Nwith the pan and the ladle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like something \Nthat stupid man would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you people! This is \Nhow you have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up all of the crew! \NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea wind blows to where, who knows? \NThe waves will be our guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O'er across the ocean's tide, \Nthe sunset is goin' wild
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the sky! Birds singing \Nin circles passing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--Men are funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funnier than Sweetpea's drunk dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but I can't top this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing out on our journey \Nto the ends of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you get it? It's like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so funny, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men stick chopsticks in their nasal cavities \Nto their mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold baskets in their hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a classless dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Belly-talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This is the specialty of Maiden Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penne gorgonzola with Sea King meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often eat Sea King meat \Nbut this is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's soft like gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? One more time!\N--No, then you won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this Sea King meat is \Nvery good! It's hard to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you doing - picking \Nand stretching my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help it! You'll \Nleave tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people who \Nwant to touch you just one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's taking too long! I wanna touch him now!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:53.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"20 gol per touch"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're so popular!\N--Luffy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do business using \Nme without asking me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Luffy-chan! Tonight is \Nour only chance to touch a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! S-Stop, you people! \NI can't eat! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where did Luffy-sama go?\N--No! He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't have gotten too far! \NLet's find him and touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only food that I could bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you can \Nreturn to your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I'm sorry that \NI got you into some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worried when you turned into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you protected us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't eaten anything and while she \Nsaid she's tired, she also can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forcing assemble thing \Nis maybe bothering her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Granny Nyon!\N--What's the matter, Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's been chased by girls of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder. They don't see men often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Granny Bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This part of the village is \Nsecluded. Stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name's not Bean!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has something to eat, so just \Nbring him tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, you like to read newspapers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo News isn't delivered to a Calm Belt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's hard to get it but since our \Nempress is a Warlord of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to know what's going \Non in the world at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's a Warlord of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Warlord of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she's \Nreally strong in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a pirate. \NDidn't you notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you read newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess became \Nempress of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a captain of the \NKuja Pirates 11 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was young but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they put a price of 80 million on \Nher head after her first expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to do with the bad reputation \NKuja had even before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government became \Ncautious about her from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they suggested that she become \None of the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, that title is about to be revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords and Navy Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are gonna fight \Nthe Whitebeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! What'll happen?! \NW-W-W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is too much to hear at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish man! \NYou don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, that was just a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle will probably happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government has made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is a man who would never \Nallow his mates to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they know this, they \Nannounced the public execution of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgaz D. Ace, a great \Ncommander of Whitebeard's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They announced the public execution of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgaz D. Ace, a great \Ncommander of Whitebeard's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace. "Fire Fist" Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... is gonna get executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a pirate called Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...became a Warlord by \Ndefeating "Fire Fist" Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government will take full \Nadvantage of this big fish they've caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--a pirate named Ace...\N--Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is my older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?! He's your brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that he was captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's gonna be executed?! \NThen, there's no chance for him to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Whitebeard wins this battle, \Nthere will be a chance for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Where are \Nthey gonna execute him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take place Marinford's town square,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where Navy Headquarters stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "in one week," which \Nmeans 6 days from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take to get to \NSabaody Archipelago from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it takes that long, then Ace will \Nbe finished before I meet my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how long will it take \Nto get to where Ace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impel Down is where he locked, and \Nit'll take a week by a pirate ship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 4 days by a navy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Navy ships are that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a current used exclusively \Nby the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a giant whirlpool which \Nconnects those three facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you open the Gate of Justice \Nat any of the three facilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the current runs inside \Nallowing you to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if the gates aren't open, \Nyou'd just keep drifting on the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate ships would rather avoid the current
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by going a long way round.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's your \Nbrother's Vivre Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it the sheet that moves \Naround that you care about so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one that Ace gave to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also known as a paper of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tells you a direction in which the \Nperson is and about their vital energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if it's that small, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got it, it was ten times bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace has his own adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to have it. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always hang on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just a scrap of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scrap of paper will bring you \Nand me together again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace won't like me rescuing him \Nsince he's stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a little side trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go and rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how reckless it would be and how \Nbig this battle is going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be like an ant blown into a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just be flicked away \Nwithout even having done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what's gonna \Nhappen! I just wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit by calmly on the \Nsidelines and let this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to rescue the most \Ninfamous prisoner in the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a chance in a million,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you better go to the Great \NPrison where he's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they move him to the \Nexecution ground in Marinford,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the navy admirals and the Seven \NWarlords will be keeping a close eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, because your brother is now \Nthe most important prisoner they have,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no doubt that they're guarding the \Nprison with the military's full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's impossible to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I care more about getting there in \Ntime than what happens after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to get there while Ace is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me a big oar, \Nand I'll paddle myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! You can't \Nget there on will alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a slim chance, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess refuses to follow the order to \Nforce the Seven Warlords of the Sea to assemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only she obeys the order,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can take advantage of it \Nand let you on their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ship? There's a navy ship here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna go and ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Nyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Enishida? Why \Nare you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god. I was going to come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snake Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has come down with an unknown illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's sick?!\N--Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock has fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Nyon tells the whole gang \Nabout this terrifying illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which has killed previous \Nempresses of Amazon Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could this illness be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Love is a Hurricane! \NLove-Love Hancock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
